{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bbc-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5104"},"text":"§ 5104.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Decisions and notices of decisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bbd-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In the case of a decision by the Secretary under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s511"},"text":"section 511 of this title","children":[],"tail":" affecting the provision of benefits to a claimant, the Secretary shall, on a timely basis, provide to the claimant (and to the claimant’s representative) notice of such decision. The notice shall include an explanation of the procedure for obtaining review of the decision."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bbe-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Each notice provided under subsection (a) shall also include all of the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bbf-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Identification of the issues adjudicated.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc0-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A summary of the evidence considered by the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc1-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A summary of the applicable laws and regulations.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc2-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Identification of findings favorable to the claimant.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc3-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" In the case of a denial, identification of elements not satisfied leading to the denial.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc4-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An explanation of how to obtain or access evidence used in making the decision.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc5-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/b/7"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7"},"text":"(7)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" If applicable, identification of the criteria that must be satisfied to grant service connection or the next higher level of compensation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc6-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary may provide notice under subsection (a) electronically if a claimant (or the claimant’s representative) elects to receive such notice electronically. A claimant (or the claimant’s representative) may revoke such an election at any time, by means prescribed by the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc7-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary shall annually—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc8-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" solicit recommendations from stakeholders on how to improve notice under this section; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bc9-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87","identifier":"/us/usc/t38/s5104/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" publish such recommendations on a publicly available website of the Department.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc3d05bca-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/tI/s115/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, title I, § 115(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/2065"},"text":"103 Stat. 2065","children":[],"tail":", § 3004; renumbered § 5104, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-05-07"},"text":"May 7, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/238"},"text":"105 Stat. 238","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/54/s14/d/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–54, § 14(d)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-06-13"},"text":"June 13, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/285"},"text":"105 Stat. 285","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/446/tXII/s1201/d/15"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–446, title XII, § 1201(d)(15)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-11-02"},"text":"Nov. 2, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/4684"},"text":"108 Stat. 4684","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/55/s2/e"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–55, § 2(e)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 2017","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/1106"},"text":"131 Stat. 1106","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/168/tVIII/s807/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–168, title VIII, § 807(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-08-10"},"text":"Aug. 10, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/1806"},"text":"136 Stat. 1806","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc3d05bcb-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc3d05bcc-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"idc3d05bcd-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Prior section 5104 was renumbered ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s8304"},"text":"section 8304 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idc3d05bce-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsecs. (c), (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/168"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–168","children":[],"tail":" added subsecs. (c) and (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2017—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/55"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–55","children":[],"tail":" amended subsec. (b) generally. Prior to amendment, subsec. (b) read as follows: “In any case where the Secretary denies a benefit sought, the notice required by subsection (a) shall also include (1) a statement of the reasons for the decision, and (2) a summary of the evidence considered by the Secretary.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1994—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/446"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–446","children":[],"tail":" substituted “section 511” for “section 211(a)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1991—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/40"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–40","children":[],"tail":" renumbered "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s3004"},"text":"section 3004 of this title","children":[],"tail":" as this section."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/54"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–54","children":[],"tail":" amended section as in effect immediately before enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/40"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–40","children":[],"tail":" by striking out “(1)” after “(a)” and substituting “(b)” for “(2)”, “subsection (a)” for “paragraph (1) of this subsection”, “(1)” for “(A)”, and “(2)” for “(B)”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idc3d05bcf-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idc3d05bd0-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2017 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/55"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–55","children":[],"tail":" applicable to all claims for which the Secretary of Veterans Affairs provides notice of a decision under this section on or after the later of 540 days after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-08-23"},"text":"Aug. 23, 2017","children":[],"tail":", or 30 days after the date on which the Secretary submits to Congress a certification of certain capabilities of the Department of Veterans Affairs to carry out the new appeals system established by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/55"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–55","children":[],"tail":" and to address appeals of decisions on legacy claims, with provision for early applicability of the new appeals system to certain claims, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/55/s2/x"},"text":"section 2(x) of Pub. L. 115–55","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s101"},"text":"section 101 of this title","children":[],"tail":", and bracketed note thereunder."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDate","id":"idc3d05bd1-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/237/tI/s115/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–237, title I, § 115(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1989-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1989","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/103/2066"},"text":"103 Stat. 2066","children":[],"tail":", provided that: "},{"tag":"quotedContent","attrib":{"origin":"/us/pl/101/237/tI/s115/b"},"text":"“Section 3004 [now 5104] of title 38, United States Code, as added by subsection (a), shall apply with respect to decisions by the Secretary of Veterans Affairs made after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-01-31"},"text":"January 31, 1990","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"idc3d05bd2-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Rule of Construction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/168"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–168","children":[],"tail":" not to be construed to apply subsec. (a) of this section to decisions of the Board of Veterans’ Appeals under chapter 71 of this title, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/168/s807/b"},"text":"section 807(b) of Pub. L. 117–168","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t38/s5100"},"text":"section 5100 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
